{"lastModified":1772726436558,"uri":"c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia\n\nBuilt by the iconic Italian shipyard in 2017, highlighted by the contrast between the metallic coloured hull and black/silver superstructure. A sleek, sporty yacht, where performance is key to the Riva Perseo; overpowered by twin 1.800 hp MAN engines, she can reach a top speed of 39 knots. The Riva Perseo is provided with 3 cabins, suitable to accomodate 6 guests. A full beam master cabin with large hull glazing to let in plenty of natural light and offering magnificent views, a VIP cabin with queen size bed and a Twin beds cabin, all with private en suite. This 23 mt yacht has a sophisticated interior with white leather sofas and teak furniture. The harmony of shapes and the elegance of space on the Riva Perseo have been matched by means of a careful, in-depth study of each and every detail and solution.","blueprint":{"name":"CHILUCE","images":["/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::927f1700-8a73-11f0-82c4-69f05950906b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a0c19a40-8a73-11f0-82c4-69f05950906b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9c9ef2a0-8a73-11f0-82c4-69f05950906b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e280a840-8a73-11f0-82c4-69f05950906b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::eebdbe90-8a73-11f0-82c4-69f05950906b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::07638f10-8a74-11f0-82c4-69f05950906b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::d5cc4e1e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0e69a790-8a74-11